title: Barbarian Active (<lvl 70)
comment_one:
Priority is "Book of the Wise" then dmg talents then "Lucky Clover" for more EXP gains.
*1 = As much as needed.
*2 = Put rest of points here.
comment_two: Go for 1 in each active skill, then 50 % in "Double Strike", max "Carry A Big Stick", then mix "Absolute Unit" and "Strength in numbers".
comment_three: Go for 1 in each active skill, then you want to max "Back to Basics",  after that max "Bear Claw" for faster clear.
notes: This is the end goal for around level 70, after that you want to invest into changes.
